# rule: plan-implement-verify
- For non-trivial tasks: (1) plan, (2) implement, (3) run checks (typecheck, tests), (4) fix, (5) summarize.
- Keep diffs small; avoid wide refactors in one step.
- Prefer repository scripts (`scripts/*.ts`) for data generation over ad-hoc code in pages.
- .env.local is implementet and correkt but invisible request if needted manual edit from user